This paper deals with pattern classification and the estimation of label class distributions, which are common topics in machine learning and statistics. The use of the Bayes classifier and the PAC setting also suggest a focus on theoretical analysis and algorithmic design. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.ST (Statistics), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
